Description: OceanEx is a blockchain-based digital asset trading platform, offering professional services to digital asset investors, traders, and liquidity providers. The platform supports a wide range of digital currencies, including Bitcoin, Ethereum, VeChain, and USDT. It uses advanced machine learning algorithms to detect attacks and safeguard assets and transactions. OceanEx provides a high-performance trading engine capable of handling large orders, optimized for high-throughput and real-time trading. The platform also offers various trading tools and investment products tailored for professional traders.
